  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "First listen and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "先听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "Why does the writer not understand the porter?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "为什么作者听不懂搬运工的话？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "I arrived in London at last.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我终于到了伦敦。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "The railway station was big, and dark.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "火车站又大又昏暗。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "I did not know the way to my hotel, so I asked a porter.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我不知道去饭店的路，于是向一名搬运工打听。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "I not only spoke English very carefully, but very clearly as well.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我不但非常认真地讲英语，而且咬字也很清楚。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "The porter, however, could not understand me.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "然而，那搬运工却听不懂我的话。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "I repeated my question several times and at last he understood.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我把问题重复了好几遍，他终于听懂了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "He answered me, but he spoke neither slowly nor clearly.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他回答了我，但既说得不慢，也说得不清楚。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "I am a foreigner, I said.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“我是外国人，”我说。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "Then he spoke slowly, but I could not understand him.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "于是他说得慢了，可我还是听不懂。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "My teacher never spoke English like that.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我的老师从来不那样讲英语。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "The porter and I looked at each other and smiled.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "搬运工和我互相看了看，都笑了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "Then he said something and I understood it.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "后来他说了一句话，我听懂了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "You'll soon learn English, he said.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“你很快就会学会英语的，”他说。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "I wonder.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我很怀疑。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "In England, each person speaks a different language.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "在英国，每个人说的似乎都是一种不同的语言。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "The English understand each other, but I don't understand them.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "英国人彼此能听懂，可我听不懂他们。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "Do they speak English?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他们说的真是英语吗？"
      }
    }
  ],
